    <h2>Why Magnesium Oil?</h2>
    <p>Magnesium is a vital mineral for the body, crucial for over 300 biochemical reactions. From improving sleep quality to enhancing muscle recovery, its benefits are extensive. However, many people don't get enough magnesium from their diet alone. This is where the Magnesium Oil Spray comes in.</p>
    <h2>The Benefits of Topical Magnesium</h2>
    <p>Applying magnesium topically can be more effective than oral supplements for certain individuals. The skin, being the largest organ, absorbs the mineral directly into the bloodstream, bypassing the digestive system. This method can be particularly beneficial for those with digestive issues or those who find oral supplements hard to tolerate.</p>
    <h3>Features of Centered AF's Magnesium Oil Spray</h3>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Pure and Natural:</strong> Sourced from the ancient Zechstein seabed in Northern Europe, known for its pure and high-quality magnesium chloride.</li>
        <li><strong>Easy Absorption:</strong> Designed for optimal absorption through the skin, delivering magnesium directly to where it's needed.</li>
        <li><strong>Soothing and Relaxing:</strong> Perfect for use after a long day or a strenuous workout, it helps soothe muscles and calm the mind.</li>
    </ul>
    <h2>Incorporating Magnesium Oil into Your Routine</h2>
    <p>Using the Magnesium Oil Spray from Centered AF is simple. Just spray it onto your skin, ideally after a shower when your pores are open, and massage gently. It's particularly effective when used on sore muscles or before bedtime to promote relaxation and better sleep.</p>
